			<article class="posts_listing post-2191 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-feature tag-christ tag-giving tag-holiday tag-jesus tag-teacher tag-volunteer" id="post-2191">
				
						
					<a href="http://www.umiteacher.com/giving-beyond-the-holiday-season/" title="Giving Beyond the Holiday Season" class="imgborder clearfix thumb listing"><img src="http://www.umiteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/80295351.jpg" class="attachment-blog_thumbnail size-blog_thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="80295351" srcset="http://www.umiteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/80295351.jpg 507w, http://www.umiteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/80295351-300x200.jpg 300w, http://www.umiteacher.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/80295351-150x100.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px" /></a>
				
				<div class="post_title_area">
										<div class="blogtitles  nodate"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.umiteacher.com/giving-beyond-the-holiday-season/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Giving Beyond the Holiday Season">Giving Beyond the Holiday Season</a></h2>
						<p class="postmeta"><a href="http://www.umiteacher.com/giving-beyond-the-holiday-season/#respond" class="commentslink" >Comments (0)</a><span>|</span><a href="http://www.umiteacher.com/giving-beyond-the-holiday-season/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Giving Beyond the Holiday Season"  class="">Read more</a></p>


						<div class="entry-content  entry-excerpt">

							<p>by Crystal McDowell In 1949, Jim Elliot penned the following: &ldquo;He is no fool who gives what he cannot keep, to gain what he cannot lose&rdquo;. Those words are no less powerful today than when he wrote them years ago. As believers we are compelled to give beyond our comfort level. We give in faith&#8230;</p>
